  "detailed_description": "Shoot, dash, and power your way through enemy lines in the arcade-style 2D side scroller, Die Erdnussbutter! Use the power of peanut butter to destroy enemy rations, battle bosses, and spread the smooth (or crunchy) flavor of freedom throughout the battlefield. Peanut butter not included.<br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4 weapons, each with their own special and ultimate abilities<br></li><li>3 stages<br></li><li>3 bosses<br></li><li>14 unique upgrades to power up with<br></li><li>Randomly generated levels for non-stop replayability</li></ul>",
